fields.headline: Constituency profile:  Liverpool Walton
fields.bodyText: A strong Labour seat, inner city, high unemployment. It is also home to two world famous football clubs, Everton and Liverpool FC Held by Peter Kilfoyle, Labour Majority 27,038 Electorate 66,745 Candidates: Conservative Stephen Horgan Lib Dem Kiron Reid Labour Peter Kilfoyle UKIP Peter Forrest
